thread.title: Murshida VA
thread.title_full: Rush Order Tees reviewed by Murshida VA

author: Murshida VA
title: Murshida VA
text:
Olivia and Michael helped me fulfill and order for 200 printed tees that was shipped to three different locations at the last moment and 2 to D.C. Area just before the inauguration. Everything was completed to spec on time; they helped me save money without sacrificing quality; and even gave me tips that will help me grow our business with their company.
I felt really cared for and supported and attended to. It's was a great experience.
